<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If you do, I'll eat you!</font>

55
00:11:41,022 --> 00:11:44,052
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">This is the first time I've seen a real spirit!</font>

56
00:11:44,052 --> 00:11:45,482
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">So they really do exist!</font>

57
00:11:45,482 --> 00:11:49,042
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Amazing! Incredible! Fantastic!</font>

58
00:11:45,482 --> 00:11:49,042
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">{\an8}So what did you think I was?</font>

59
